#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thig2.1:3.1"
msgid "1. Abhirūpanandātherīgāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "thig2.1:4.1"
msgid "<span class=\"cross\" title=\"^thig5.4#1 [Sundarīnandātherīgāthā] | ^thi-ap18#66 [Khemātherīapadāna]\" id=\"note13\">*</span> <a class=\"sc\" id=\"1\"></a><a class=\"verse-num-sc\" id=\"verse-num-sc19\"></a><a class=\"verse-num-pts\" id=\"verse-num-pts19\"></a>“Āturaṃ asuciṃ pūtiṃ,"
msgstr "Nandā, see the body as"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.1:4.2"
msgid "passa nande samussayaṃ;"
msgstr "Diseased, dirty, stinking"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.1:4.3"
msgid "Asubhāya cittaṃ bhāvehi,"
msgstr "Meditate on the unattractive,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.1:4.4"
msgid "ekaggaṃ susamāhitaṃ."
msgstr "Unified, serene in samādhi;"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc20"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts20"></a>
msgctxt "thig2.1:5.1"
msgid "Animittañca bhāvehi,"
msgstr "Meditate on the signless,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.1:5.2"
msgid "mānānusayamujjaha;"
msgstr "Throw out the tendency to conceit,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.1:5.3"
msgid "Tato mānābhisamayā,"
msgstr "Having fully understood conceit"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig2.1:5.4"
msgid "upasantā carissasī”ti."
msgstr "You'll wander at peace"

#. </p></blockquote><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a>
msgctxt "thig2.1:6.1"
msgid "<span class=\"var\" title=\"itthaṃ sudaṃ bhagavā nandaṃ sikkhamānaṃ imāhi gāthāhi abhiṇhaṃ ovadati (s2, s3, pts1-2) | itthaṃ sudaṃ bhagavā abhirūpanandaṃ sikkhamānaṃ imāhi gāthāhi abhiṇhaṃ ovadatīti (mr)\" id=\"note14\">Itthaṃ sudaṃ abhirūpanandā therī gāthāyo abhāsitthāti</span>."
